			<h2 class="article-poster-vertical__headline">
				<a href="https://breakermag.com/we-asked-crypto-news-outlets-if-theyd-take-money-to-cover-a-project-more-than-half-said-yes/">
					We Asked Crypto News Outlets If They&#8217;d Take Money to Cover a Project. More Than Half Said Yes				</a>
			</h2>

										<div class="article-poster-vertical__byline">
					<a href="https://breakermag.com/author/cfaife/" title="Posts by Corin Faife" class="author url fn" rel="author">By Corin Faife</a>				</div>
			
					<div class="article-poster__posted-date">
			10.25.2018		</div>
	
		</div>

